<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 16:09:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列在加沙最血腥的一天引发了人们对接下来会发生什么的疑问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-bloodiest-day-in-gaza-raises-questions-over-what-comes-next/0000018d-36ad-d6f3-a7af-3fefd1e90000</link><description>一次事件中 21 名以色列国防军士兵丧生，证明了涉及大量爆炸物的地面行动的危险性。它还对在边境建立缓冲区的优点提出质疑</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 15:19:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israels-bloodiest-day-in-gaza-raises-questions-over-what-comes-next/0000018d-36ad-d6f3-a7af-3fefd1e90000</guid></item><item><title>真主党两周内第二次袭击以色列北部的以色列国防军空军基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-hits-idf-airbase-in-northern-israel-for-second-time-in-two-weeks/0000018d-368a-dbf8-abdf-bede69f70000</link><description>真主党表示，发射这些导弹是为了回应以色列暗杀真主党和圣城旅指挥官的事件，并在检测到以色列空军基地存在“漏洞”后；以色列国防军报告“轻微损坏”</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 14:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-hits-idf-airbase-in-northern-israel-for-second-time-in-two-weeks/0000018d-368a-dbf8-abdf-bede69f70000</guid></item><item><title>“总统不能否决我的投票”：拜登在首次民主党初选中面临加沙考验</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-president-cant-veto-my-vote-biden-faces-gaza-test-in-first-democratic-primary/0000018d-35c2-d6df-adcf-35d3f6580000</link><description>一些活动人士发誓要在周二的新罕布什尔州初选中写下“停火”，以抗议总统乔·拜登对以色列与哈马斯战争的态度。由于党内不和，拜登的名字根本没有出现在选票上</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:07:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-president-cant-veto-my-vote-biden-faces-gaza-test-in-first-democratic-primary/0000018d-35c2-d6df-adcf-35d3f6580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列清空了北部地区。现在官员们担心撤离人员在战后不会返回家园</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-emptied-its-north-now-officials-fear-evacuees-wont-return-home-after-the-war/0000018d-35df-d6df-adcf-35df4bb70000</link><description>加沙战争期间，居住在黎巴嫩边境附近的近8万人被疏散或逃离；一项调查显示，只有 60% 的人确定自己想回国</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 13:01:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-emptied-its-north-now-officials-fear-evacuees-wont-return-home-after-the-war/0000018d-35df-d6df-adcf-35df4bb70000</guid></item><item><title>与 10 月 7 日受害者一起工作的高级精神科医生：以色列需要希望的处方</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/senior-psychiatrist-working-with-october-7-victims-israel-needs-a-prescription-of-hope/0000018d-35d3-db8f-a7df-37f3de210000</link><description>什洛莫·门德洛维奇教授表示，仍然很难估计有多少以色列人会患上创伤后应激障碍（“估计有 60,000 到 600,000 个新病例”）。他解释了为什么团体治疗可能是一场灾难，并建议以色列必须采取哪些措施才能康复</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 12:45:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/senior-psychiatrist-working-with-october-7-victims-israel-needs-a-prescription-of-hope/0000018d-35d3-db8f-a7df-37f3de210000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队围攻汗尤尼斯，数千名流离失所的加沙人逃往南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-besieges-khan-yunis-as-thousands-of-displaced-gazans-flee-further-south/0000018d-363b-d81e-abdf-3e3f65480000</link><description>以色列军队表示，他们正在深入城市，打击哈马斯的关键地点，居民报告称，士兵包围了两家医院，并阻止医疗队到达医院</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 12:43:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-besieges-khan-yunis-as-thousands-of-displaced-gazans-flee-further-south/0000018d-363b-d81e-abdf-3e3f65480000</guid></item><item><title>从加沙获释的人质称哈马斯对待女性人质“像玩偶一样”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hostage-released-from-gaza-says-hamas-treated-female-hostages-like-dolls/0000018d-35d9-db8f-a7df-37fb5cf70000</link><description>“首相和内阁不会因为她们怀孕而归来感到不安吗？” ■ 在以色列议会性暴力和性别暴力受害者会议上，被扣押在加沙的女性人质的家人恳求释放她们</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 11:13:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/hostage-released-from-gaza-says-hamas-treated-female-hostages-like-dolls/0000018d-35d9-db8f-a7df-37fb5cf70000</guid></item><item><title>21名士兵丧生，这是以色列对加沙发动地面进攻以来最严重的事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/21-soldiers-killed-in-deadliest-incident-for-israel-since-start-of-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018d-35af-d81e-abdf-3daf470e0000</link><description>部队在距离边境 600 米的建筑物中埋设地雷，将其夷为平地。哈马斯战士向守卫士兵的坦克和建筑物发射火箭弹，导致士兵倒塌</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 10:34:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/21-soldiers-killed-in-deadliest-incident-for-israel-since-start-of-gaza-ground-offensive/0000018d-35af-d81e-abdf-3daf470e0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争助推埃尔多安竞选，土耳其与哈马斯保持密切关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-is-giving-a-boost-to-erdogan-election-campaign/0000018d-3556-d81e-abdf-3d5e04970000</link><description>当埃尔多安利用亲巴勒斯坦情绪让他的政党在即将举行的地方选举中取得胜利时，土耳其发现自己被排除在有关加沙未来的讨论之外。尽管如此，该国仍将在哈马斯的命运中发挥关键作用</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 09:29:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/the-gaza-is-giving-a-boost-to-erdogan-election-campaign/0000018d-3556-d81e-abdf-3d5e04970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：完成对汗尤尼斯的围困；真主党：以色列北部空军基地遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-live/three-israeli-officers-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-345d-d6df-adcf-35dd49d60000</link><description>哈马斯管理的卫生部：过去 24 小时内以色列的袭击造成 195 人死亡 ■ 以色列军队在加沙边境附近的建筑物上进行了拆除。哈马斯枪手向附近的一辆坦克发射火箭弹，同时发生爆炸，导致里面有士兵的建筑物倒塌 ■ 报道：卡车在叙利亚和伊拉克边境附近遭到袭击并爆炸 ■ 据报道，以色列已向哈马斯提出建议据 Axios 报道，通过调解，其中包括作为新协议的一部分暂停战斗长达两个月</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 03:34:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article-live/three-israeli-officers-killed-in-southern-gaza-strip-combat/0000018d-345d-d6df-adcf-35dd49d60000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列官员因涉嫌向巴勒斯坦人出售数千份入境许可证而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-officers-arrested-on-suspicion-of-selling-entry-permits-to-palestinians/0000018d-333e-d6df-adcf-33bf7c6d0000</link><description>两名主要嫌疑人是一名职业军官和他的父亲，警方在他的家中发现了 74 万谢克尔现金和 121 块金锭</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 22:25:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/three-israeli-officers-arrested-on-suspicion-of-selling-entry-permits-to-palestinians/0000018d-333e-d6df-adcf-33bf7c6d0000</guid></item><item><title>据报道，内塔尼亚胡告诉人质家属：以色列愿意为新协议做出让步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-reportedly-told-hostages-families-israel-would-make-concessions-for-new-deal/0000018d-332d-d81e-abdf-3b2dcf850000</link><description>消息人士称，总理似乎愿意在释放巴勒斯坦囚犯的数量和身份问题上做出妥协——300人在内塔尼亚胡耶路撒冷的家外示威</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 22:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-23/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-reportedly-told-hostages-families-israel-would-make-concessions-for-new-deal/0000018d-332d-d81e-abdf-3b2dcf850000</guid></item><item><title>周一，三名以色列国防军军官在加沙战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/three-israeli-army-officers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-monday/0000018d-328a-d81e-abdf-3a8e3dfe0000</link><description>这三人分别是大卫·纳蒂·阿尔法西少校、伊莱·利维少校和埃亚尔·梅沃拉奇·特维托上尉，均在加沙地带南部的一场战斗中阵亡。据军方称，自地面行动开始以来，已有200名以色列士兵在加沙丧生</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:38:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/three-israeli-army-officers-killed-in-gaza-combat-on-monday/0000018d-328a-d81e-abdf-3a8e3dfe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外长通过视频回避欧盟关于两国解决方案的讨论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/israels-foreign-minister-evades-eu-discussion-on-two-state-solution-with-video-show/0000018d-32a4-db8f-a7df-32f7bc410000</link><description>以色列外长以色列·卡茨在访问布鲁塞尔期间参加了中东问题的讨论</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/israels-foreign-minister-evades-eu-discussion-on-two-state-solution-with-video-show/0000018d-32a4-db8f-a7df-32f7bc410000</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克与本·夏皮罗在奥斯维辛：又一场愤世嫉俗的粉饰表演</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-22/ty-article/.highlight/elon-musk-with-ben-shapiro-in-auschwitz-another-cynical-whitewashing-performance/0000018d-326b-db8f-a7df-32fb97df0000</link><description>马斯克从这些展示中得到的好处是显而易见的，但对欧洲犹太协会等东道主来说有什么好处就不言而喻了</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:14:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-22/ty-article/.highlight/elon-musk-with-ben-shapiro-in-auschwitz-another-cynical-whitewashing-performance/0000018d-326b-db8f-a7df-32fb97df0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管因以色列与哈马斯战争而取消航班，本古里安机场的乘客数量仍增加了 10%</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/number-of-passengers-at-ben-gurion-airport-rises-10-despite-israel-hamas-war/0000018d-3246-d81e-abdf-3a4e9e540000</link><description>虽然大多数外国航空公司决定停止或限制往返以色列的航班，但 2022 年至 2023 年间乘客总数增加了 10%</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 19:13:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/number-of-passengers-at-ben-gurion-airport-rises-10-despite-israel-hamas-war/0000018d-3246-d81e-abdf-3a4e9e540000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队：汗尤尼斯的激烈战斗预计将持续数天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-intense-fighting-in-khan-yunis-expected-to-last-several-days/0000018d-3215-d81e-abdf-3a1d5a440000</link><description>汗尤尼斯是加沙南部最大的城市，也是哈马斯的据点，最近几周一直是战斗中心。数以千计的平民使日益激烈的战斗变得更加复杂，以色列鼓励他们向南迁移到拉法</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 18:41:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-intense-fighting-in-khan-yunis-expected-to-last-several-days/0000018d-3215-d81e-abdf-3a1d5a440000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡已经没有谎言了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-running-out-of-lies/0000018d-31d5-d81e-abdf-39dda0270000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡面临的两大压力——呼吁达成人质协议和美国针对加沙的“事后”计划——正变得难以承受。他们即将向他汇合</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 17:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-is-running-out-of-lies/0000018d-31d5-d81e-abdf-39dda0270000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和美国正在就两国解决方案进行虚假辩论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-u-s-are-engaging-in-a-bogus-debate-over-the-two-state-solution/0000018d-3176-d81e-abdf-397e98c40000</link><description>美国对与以色列一起建立巴勒斯坦国的前景的关注是内塔尼亚胡精心策划的策略的一部分，内塔尼亚胡又故技重施。两国解决方案现在不可能实现，拜登政府知道这一点</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 17:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-u-s-are-engaging-in-a-bogus-debate-over-the-two-state-solution/0000018d-3176-d81e-abdf-397e98c40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长威胁起诉《国土报》，称其在恐怖袭击后“在鲜血上跳舞”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-threatens-to-sue-haaretz-for-saying-he-was-dancing-on-blood/0000018d-31cb-d81e-abdf-39cfd0700000</link><description>尤阿夫·基什（Yoav Kisch）在谈到拉阿纳纳恐怖袭击后《国土报》发表的两篇文章时表示，“将教育部长描绘成在死者和伤者的鲜血上跳舞的人构成了严重的诽谤”。他的律师要求《国土报》删除这些文章并道歉</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jan 2024 17:22:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-threatens-to-sue-haaretz-for-saying-he-was-dancing-on-blood/0000018d-31cb-d81e-abdf-39cfd0700000</guid></item></channel></rss>